<h1>About NCalc 101</h1>
<p>
	NCalc 101 is a simple web application that allows you to try out the NCalc expression evaluator.
</p>
<p>
	It was inspired by <a href="https://regex101.com/">RegEx 101</a>, which is a great tool for trying out regular expressions.
</p>
<p>
	NCalc 101 is written in Blazor WebAssembly and is open source. You can find the source code <a href="https://github.com/panoramicdata/PanoramicData.NCalc101/">on Github</a>.
</p>
<p>
	NCalc 101 was written by <a href="https://www.panoramicdata.com/">Panoramic Data</a>.
</p>
